        <h1>Fitness Plan (18-25 Underweight)</h1>
        
        <h2>Diet Plan</h2>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Breakfast:</strong> Scrambled eggs, whole wheat toast, and a banana smoothie.</li>
            <li><strong>Lunch:</strong> Grilled chicken with quinoa and roasted vegetables.</li>
            <li><strong>Snacks:</strong> Greek yogurt with almonds and honey.</li>
            <li><strong>Dinner:</strong> Baked salmon with sweet potatoes and steamed broccoli.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Gym Routine</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Strength training (full body) 3-4 times a week.</li>
            <li>Cardio (light jogging or cycling) 2 times a week.</li>
            <li>Flexibility and core exercises (yoga, planks, stretching).</li>
        </ul>
